    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable choice for someone looking for a functional daily driver. While it remains mechanically sound for everyday use, there are clear signs of wear consistent with its age. The exterior shows some fading in the paint and a few minor dents, while the interior has some visible staining on the upholstery and a cracked dashboard. It starts and runs reliably, though it may require some minor maintenance in the near future to keep it in peak operating condition. It is a solid, honest car for someone who prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
