    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project seekers! This vehicle is the perfect canvas for someone looking to roll up their sleeves and bring a car back to life. While it currently requires significant mechanical work and cosmetic attention, it represents a fantastic opportunity to own a vehicle at a budget-friendly price. If you\u2019re looking for a rewarding weekend project with great potential, this is the one for you!",
