    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies consistent performance and aesthetic integrity. This unit has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure mechanical excellence and long-term reliability. Offering a balanced synthesis of comfort and durability, it remains a premier choice for the discerning driver seeking a dependable, high-caliber automotive investment.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
