    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hi there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride and is still in really solid shape, perfect for someone who wants a dependable vehicle without the brand-new price tag! It drives super smoothly and has been well-loved, so it's totally ready for its next adventure with you. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions\u2014I'd love to chat!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This 911 Carrera features the highly evolved 3.6L M96 flat-six, delivering 320hp with a linear power delivery and exceptional throttle response across the rev range. The 6-speed manual transaxle provides crisp gear engagement, complemented by a chassis that retains its precise factory suspension geometry for neutral handling. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including an IMS bearing retrofit and a fresh rear main seal (RMS). The braking system utilizes four-piston monobloc calipers for consistent thermal management under load. This 996.2 chassis is a mechanically sound example, offering a visceral driving experience with high operational integrity.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Regularly serviced. Clean title. Runs well. Minor cosmetic wear.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that serves as a perfect example of a well-cared-for daily driver. The exterior finish retains a high-gloss luster, though a close inspection reveals minor, honest stone chips on the front fascia consistent with highway use. The body panels are straight with consistent gaps throughout. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in. The premium upholstery is supple and free of any rips or stains, showing only light, natural creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster. All electronic features\u2014including the dual-zone climate control, infotainment system, and heated seats\u2014operate flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is turn-key ready. The engine idles smoothly and pulls strongly through all gears, backed by a documented service history. Recent maintenance includes a fresh synthetic oil change, a new cabin air filter, and a brake system flush. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, mounted on wheels that show virtually no curb rash. This car offers a refined driving experience and represents a fantastic value for someone seeking reliability and comfort without the premium of a showroom-new price tag.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this distinguished vehicle, an exemplary specimen that balances sophisticated engineering with proven durability. This unit has been maintained to a rigorous standard, ensuring that its mechanical integrity remains beyond reproach. While it bears the minor, honest character marks consistent with careful ownership, its performance and interior refinement continue to offer a premium driving experience. This is a strategic acquisition for the professional seeking a reliable, high-caliber vehicle that represents exceptional market value.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    }
